      "content": "I spent fifteen years on this. Every paper, every grant, every late night in the lab... it was all based on a fundamental error I didn't catch until yesterday. It wasn't just a mistake, it was a delusion. I've built my entire identity on a foundation of nothing. There's no way to fix this. There's just no point in being here anymore now that I know I'm a fraud.",
